text:
Look I am actually from the future, I time travelled, the details are unimportant. I can tell you this is a really stupid idea.

I should probably also disclose I think it's okay to lie about whether or not a person is a time traveler under certain completely benign circumstances. One such circumstance would be reducing undue economic hardship on otherwise decent people in a pandemic.
